getHelperType

IHelperType getHelperType(java.lang.String name,
                          java.lang.String modelUri)
Locates a helper type given its name and its model URI.

Parameters:
name - The helper type's name; must not be null
modelUri - the helper type's model URI; must not be null
Returns:
the located helper type or null if the helper type name and model URI pair was not located in the helper type registry

getAllHelperTypes

IHelperType[] getAllHelperTypes()
Locates all helper types. Abstract types will be excluded.

Returns:
all helper types; never null

getAllHelperTypes

Locates all helper types.

Parameters:

Returns:
all helper types; never null
